=User:Immanuelle/lucky direction|13=User:Immanuelle/Toshitoku-shin|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 歳徳神}} associated with Ren is north-northwest, slightly north (345 degrees). ==Sexagenary cycles containing Mizunoe (壬)== {{wiktionary|壬}} {| class="wikitable alternance droite" |{{ill|Yang Water Monkey|ja|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|壬申|zh|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|壬申|ko|임신|fr|Singe d'eau|de|Wasser-Affe|en|Water Monkey|lt=壬申 (Yang Water Monkey)|lt_ko=임신|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Monkey|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Water Horse|ja|1=Yang Water Horse|2=ja|壬午|zh|1=Yang Water Horse|2=ja|壬午|ko|임오|fr|Cheval d'eau|de|Wasser-Pferd|en|Water Horse|lt=壬午 (Yang Water Horse)|lt_ko=임오|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Horse|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Water Dragon|ja|1=Yang Water Dragon|2=ja|壬辰|zh|1=Yang Water Dragon|2=ja|壬辰|ko|임진|fr|Dragon d'eau|de|Wasser-Drache|en|Water Dragon|lt=壬辰 (Yang Water Dragon)|lt_ko=임진|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Dragon|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Water Tiger|ja|1=Yang Water Tiger|2=ja|壬寅|zh|1=Yang Water Tiger|2=ja|壬寅|ko|임인|fr|Tigre d'eau|de|Wasser-Tiger|en|Water Tiger|lt=壬寅 (Yang Water Tiger)|lt_ko=임인|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Tiger|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Water Rat|ja|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|zh|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|ko|임자|fr|Rat d'eau|de|Wasser-Ratte|en|Water Rat|lt=壬子 (Yang Water Rat)|lt_ko=임자|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;font-size:100%" |{{ill|Yang Water Dog|ja|1=Yang Water Dog|2=ja|壬戌|zh|1=Yang Water Dog|2=ja|壬戌|ko|임술|fr|Chien d'eau|de|Wasser-Hund|en|Water Dog|lt=壬戌 (Yang Water Dog)|lt_ko=임술|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Dog|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
